OL,6,F"Households could be looking at #360
OL,7,Fper year in additional costs. That's
OL,8,Fwhen you take into consideration the
OL,9,Fincrease to the energy price cap,
OL,10,Fhigher water bills, higher broadband,
OL,11,Fmobile phone, TV license and car tax."
OL,12,F- AMY KNIGHT - Personal Finance
OL,13,FExpert, NerdWallet UK
OL,15,FNearly 9 in 10 councils in England
OL,16,Fhave increased their council tax by
OL,17,Fthe maximum permitted 4.99% from the
OL,18,Ffirst of April.
