OL,6,FThe Local Government Association told
OL,7,Fus: "Councils strive to recover unpaid
OL,8,Ftax as sympathetically as possible.
OL,9,FLocal welfare schemes run by councils,
OL,10,Fincluding council tax relief and the
OL,11,FHousehold Support Fund, are also
OL,12,Favailable alongside targeted
OL,13,Fgovernment help. Anyone having trouble
OL,14,Fpaying their council bills should get
OL,15,Fin touch with their local authority
OL,16,Ffor financial help and advice as soon
OL,17,Fas possible."
