OL,6,FIn April, water bills went up on
OL,7,Faverage 26% across the country. The
OL,8,Fbiggest rise since privatisation of
OL,9,Fwater companies more than 30 years
OL,10,Fago. Jo Obsborn is from Waterwise -
OL,11,Fwhich helps people save money on their
OL,12,Fwater bills.
OL,14,FA washing machine typically uses
OL,15,Faround 50 litres of water per load. So
OL,16,Fcutting out unnecessary laundry is an
OL,17,Feasy win. You can also save a lot of
OL,18,Fwater in the bathroom.
