OL,6,F"If you've got a family of 4 and you
OL,7,Fleave the tap running when you brush
OL,8,Fyour teeth, you can use a whole bath
OL,9,Ffull of water a day. So it's a really
OL,10,Fquick, easy way to make sure you save
OL,11,Fwater." JO OSBORN - Head of Policy and
OL,12,FResearch, Waterwise
OL,14,FWith all of our essential bills on the
OL,15,Frise, and the future of the money
OL,16,Fwe've saved uncertain - it seems we
OL,17,Fall might have to work a bit harder to
OL,18,Fkeep our budgets on track.
